        <div class="verdict">⭐ Rating: 4.1/5 — Best for small residential builders who want takeoff + PM in one affordable tool</div>

        <p>Buildxact is an Australian-founded construction software company that has built a loyal following among small-to-mid residential builders and remodelers — particularly those who find Buildertrend's price prohibitive but need more than estimating spreadsheets.</p>

        <p>The platform combines digital takeoff, estimating, and basic project management in a single subscription that starts significantly cheaper than the major US platforms. Here's the honest evaluation.</p>

